  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the feasibility of conducting a large hospital based
      case control study of the role of dioxins and dioxinlike polychlorinated dibenzofurans
      (PCDFs) and polychlorinated biphenyls (PCBs).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
